videos.description: After Jordan Bohannon misses a 3-pointer, Tyler Cook gets the rebound and rips a dunk.
videos.headline: Cook makes noise with jam

videos.description: On Jordan Bohannon's inbound, Tyler Cook pushes the ball right into the basket before it hits the ground.
videos.headline: Cook crushes monster slam
